The Chef really has some of the best fwends around. Back when The Chef found out his book sales were quite low, he schemed up a few ways to drive sales but also placed a few phone calls to close friends to ask for advice. The support from fwends meant so much to The Chef he made it the subject of his second bloven mitt ceweal box theater performance.

Please enjoy the slideshow as if you were there that night, Cheffy put so much thought and work into this recreation of the event (he even had sprigs of rosemary and thyme roasting nearby for smell!) and it would mean so much to him for people to enjoy the “meal” as if they were there!
.
.
Also big thanks to all chefs friends and attendees it meant so much to him to have all his friends in one space!
.
.
